org.dataconservancy.dcs.ingest.services.util

Class ElmSipStager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dataconservancy.dcs.ingest.services.util.ElmSipStager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.dataconservancy.dcs.ingest.SipStager

    public class ElmSipStager
extends Object
implements org.dataconservancy.dcs.ingest.SipStager
    Sip stager based on underlying ELM entity and metadata stores.

    Used for durably storing, accessing, and removing staged sips using underlying ELM components.

    Configuration

    setEntityStore(EntityStore)
    Required. SIPs are stored in the entity store.
    setMetadataStore(MetadataStore)
    Required. SIP ids are stored in the metadata store.
    setIdentifierService(IdService)
    Required. Used for identifying a staged sip.
    setIdentifierService(IdService)
    Required. Used for identifying a staged sip.
    setModelBuilder(DcsModelBuilder)
    Required. Used for serializing SIPs in the store.
